Product description

The Braun MQ100 Multiquick 1 Hand Blender is the kitchen tool you need to prepare your favorite meals. This device looks trendy with its slim structure and white finish and is quite easy to operate. It comes with a 600ml plastic beaker for easy measurement of your ingredients. The appliance ensures all your foods are blended precisely and quickly with its PowerBell technology. Blending ingredients often leave the kitchen messy, but not with this blender. It has a unique anti splash design that ensures your kitchen counter remains spotless, even after prolonged use, Invoice is an proof for warranty .

Key Features

Simple speed activation

Compact and handy

Beaker

PowerBell technology

A Blender with a Personality

This hand blender looks smart and stylish with its super thin body and elegant white color. It has a large green speed activation button at the front that requires only a touch to get the device started. The blender’s ergonomic design allows you to operate it with just one hand. And when not in use, this soup hand blender can stand elegantly in any corner of your kitchen.

The Secret Behind its Perfect Results

The Braun blender incorporates PowerBell technology that delivers perfectly even blending results. The blades of the appliance are made up of ultra hard stainless steel that are angled in opposite direction to reduce suction. The floral bell shape of the shell helps in drawing the ingredients towards the angled blades, resulting in instant blending, Invoice is an proof for warranty .

Bring home this stylish, black Braun Multiquick 7 Hand Blender and equip your kitchen with the tools needed to prepare all your favorite dishes. This hand blender is an ideal solution for all your blending, whipping, and ice crushing needs. It has a sturdy build, smart speed control, and employs revolutionary technology that gets you the desired outcomes effeciently. You can process the ingredients for all of your favorite recipes with one hand while changing the speed simultaneously. Also, this Braun hand mixer is available with a range of accessories that cater to both large and small food quantities. It has a powerful 750W motor and is made using sturdy materials that perform well for years to come.

Key Features

Smart Speed

PowerBell design for perfect blending results

Thermal cut-off

Powerful 750 W motor

Convenience and Performance

The Braun Multiquick 7 Hand Blender is ergonomically designed to make mixing, chopping or crushing ice comfortable and quick. It features an extra large speed button positioned near the soft grip handle to make it easy to hold and control. Also, this hand blender uses Braun’s patented Power Bell feature; a combination of hard stainless steel blades and a unique blending bell shape that guarantees the best mixing performance every time.

Highly Functional

Set up dinner in no time with the help of this Braun Multiquick 7 hand blender that will expand your mastery of the culinary arts. It has innovative features such as Easy Click accessories that allow the hand blender's shaft to be detached easily. The anti splash metal shaft makes for a neat kitchen even after you've prepared your favorite chutneys. Also, this blender has a powerful 750W motor that ensures an excellent performance that remains silent. All of Brauns accessories and parts are made out of BPA free plastic to ensure a safe and healthy cooking environment.

Product description

Choose the Braun Multiquick 5 Vario MQ5035 Hand Blender to enhance your meal preparation experience. This 750W blender gives exceptional results in less time with its powerful and surprisingly silent performance. When you have this blender in hand, you can prepare a large variety of meals easily as it is capable of chopping, mincing, and slicing. It provides 21 different speed options, which can be selected with a simple thumb gesture on its speed wheel. You can attach and detach the appliance effortlessly with its EasyClick System.

Key Features

Brand: Braun

Provides All Types of Food Mixing

The Braun Multiquick 5 hand blender incorporates the patented, cutting edge PowerBell technology. This is a combination of ultra sharp stainless steel blades and a unique bell shaped blending shaft that provides even chopping results and lump free, pure blends. The Braun hand blender includes various attachments that remove the need to clutter up your kitchen with different appliances for various needs. It has a kneading hook that softens and blends even the heaviest of dough. Its stainless steel ice crushing knife delivers superb smashing of ice cubes. The 500ml chopper lets you cut hard ingredients such as herbs, onions, etc. effortlessly. Apart from this, it also shreds, slices, purees, and minces your food efficiently.

Turn the Wheel of Speed

The 750W Braun Multiquick 5 Vario blender works with a powerful yet silent motor that adds a boost of speed to its efficient performance; thus, giving you quick and even results every time. It offers 21 speed options to help you choose the desirable pace at which you want the food to be sliced or blended. It features a one hand speed wheel that can be controlled with your thumb. This offers a seamless change of speed even during operation.

Product description

Quickly blend your favorite ingredients to make a glass of healthy shake, thanks to the Russell Hobbs 21350-56 Mix And Go Blender. The unique auto-start design does not require any switches. You can press to pulse and twist the container to blend. This Russell Hobbs blending appliance comes with two 600ml bottles in which you can pour the refreshing drink so that you can have it on the go. These bottles also contain unique cool tubes that rest inside the bottle so that you can have a nice, cold and fresh drink even hours after blending. In addition to this, you can also put the Russell Hobbs blender and its attachments in a dishwasher for effective and quick cleaning. Furthermore, the sturdy and non-slip rubber feet provide stability to the appliance.

Key Features

300 Watts

2 x 600ml bottles

2 x Drink bottle lids

2 x Cool tubes

Pressure activated auto start

Dishwasher safe parts

Nonslip rubber feet for stability

Auto-start Design

This Russell Hobbs blending appliance boasts of a unique design. You do not have to press any switch for making the appliance work. You can simply press the top of this appliance for making it pulse and twist it for blending.

Drink on the Go

This Russell Hobbs blender comes with two storing bottles. You can pour the freshly blended smoothie, yogurt, or juice in these bottles so that you can have the drink on the go if you are in a hurry.

Innovative Cool Tube

The two 600ml storage cups of this Russell Hobbs blending appliance have an innovative cool tube inside them. These tubes keep the stored drink chilled. Thus, your smoothie or juice remains fresh and cold even if you have it a few hours after packing it in the bottle.
